      "content": "but he's really insistent that it's just the jet lag and the long flight sitting in the seat. he's actually feeling a bit better now that he's sat down and had some water. wouldn't it be more likely that it's just dehydration or exhaustion from the travel? i don't want to freak him out or make a huge deal out of nothing if he just needs a nap.",
